data.description: Several bonus features here- just under 13 acres! Sought after school district! Great cul-de-sac location- gorgeous subdivision with wildlife all around in the woods and valleys. Welcome Home to Carla Lane! Open to a large open concept open to dining area, kitchen and eat in breakfast area. The living room offers wood burning fireplace and vaulted ceiling. Kitchen has lots of cabinetry and breakfast area has walk out to the deck overlooking back yard. Large main floor laundry room off the kitchen- beautiful primary suite with en suite bathroom -double vanity, shower/tub combo with jetted tub! Divided floor plan gives lots of privacy- bedrooms 2 and 3 are good sized rooms with nice size closets- and hallway bath is full bath with tub/shower combo. Lower level has rough in for another bathroom and egress window for ease of creating a 4th bedroom- unfinished and ready for you! Acreage is gorgeous- check out the photos to see the back of property and hurry to see this one!
